Privacy Policy

YouTube Client API

  • HermitCraft.com uses a YouTube API Client that uses YouTube API Services. By using HermitCraft.com, users are agreeing to be bound by the YouTube Terms of Service. The API Client is internal and does not use visitor information. The API Client retrieves publicly accessable data about videos and stores this data in it's database. This information is used to display video information on this website and is not shared externally.
  • YouTube's Terms of Service
